name: Blue Archive - Ajitani Hifumi / 阿慈谷ヒフミ / 阿慈谷日富美  (swimsuit/school uniform)
description:
Weight = 0.75~0.95 , I prefer 0.85.

It's trained with 2 style of clothes at the same time.

So you can use hifumi \(school uniform\) or hifumi \(swimsuit\) to choose the style you want

Also, it's trained with nsfw pictures. use nsfw to draw her. By the way, small breasts is easy to draw nsfw picture.

And, if you don't add clothes tags, it seems more possible to draw nude picture.

If you want to change the clothes, delete hifumi \(school uniform) and hifumi \(swimsuit\), keep hifumi \(blue archive\) , then you can pick tags of clothes you want to change freely.

Use 512*768 to draw half body, 768*1152 to draw almost full body, 1024*768 to draw girl with environment.

Some useful tags to draw the original Hifumi :

girl : halo, long light brown hair, low twintails, yellow eyes, open mouth, blush, smill, looking at viewer

school uniform : school uniform, black pantyhose, blue pleated skirt, bag, long sleeves, shoes, serafuku. ( shoes will make it draw full body, which is likely to draw bad picture.Had batter no use full body)

swimsuit : swimsuit, white frilled bikini, sunglasses, bag, collarbone

If some clothes be drawn but you don't want. Use tags above as negative prompt

modelVersions.name: v2 - tag_prune - no_reg
modelVersions.description:
When training, tags such as long light brown hair, low twintails, yellow eyes were deleted.

No use reg images.
